WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.900
=Episode 31=

01:41.570 --> 01:42.520
Father,

01:42.520 --> 01:43.410
why have you come out?

01:43.410 --> 01:44.290
Father.

01:44.290 --> 01:45.380
Song Shijun,

01:46.260 --> 01:48.210
I want you to pay with blood!

01:55.210 --> 01:57.020
Song Shijun killed the witness.

01:57.020 --> 01:58.290
Seize the murderer.

02:02.690 --> 02:03.900
What should we do, Zhao?

02:03.900 --> 02:04.930
Should we go find Master?

02:06.620 --> 02:07.620
Calm down.

02:07.620 --> 02:08.730
Everyone, calm down.

02:11.340 --> 02:13.010
There's no time. Save him first.

02:22.730 --> 02:23.570
Take him and go.

02:30.260 --> 02:31.690
Yang Heying, you useless fool.

02:32.570 --> 02:34.380
Last year, I beat you.

02:34.380 --> 02:35.570
You still haven't improved.

02:35.570 --> 02:36.933
Cai Zhao, you wretched girl.

02:36.944 --> 02:38.261
You're a traitor like Song Shijun,

02:38.272 --> 02:39.516
colluding with the demonic sect.

02:44.500 --> 02:45.340
Go help Yuzhi.

02:45.980 --> 02:46.820
Sure.

02:52.360 --> 02:53.073
Xingjia,

02:53.084 --> 02:54.230
did you bring the duck feed?

02:54.290 --> 02:55.130
I did.

02:55.610 --> 02:56.450
Chase them.

03:22.010 --> 03:22.850
How is he?

03:23.340 --> 03:25.100
Yuzhi was poisoned
with purple vine poison.

03:25.100 --> 03:26.850
I heard Uncle Lei mention it.

03:26.850 --> 03:29.260
This poison is unique
to the Blood Marsh Forest.

03:29.260 --> 03:30.460
It seals the meridians.

03:30.470 --> 03:31.340
Within two days,

03:31.340 --> 03:32.489
the victim will die.

03:32.500 --> 03:33.340
Is there an antidote?

03:33.699 --> 03:34.902
Guangtian Sect should have it.

03:34.980 --> 03:36.010
Let's go back.

03:36.010 --> 03:36.850
We can't.

03:37.060 --> 03:38.130
We'll only die faster.

03:38.690 --> 03:40.410
This whole matter has been strange.

03:40.850 --> 03:42.730
The people who refined corpse slaves

03:42.730 --> 03:44.290
should have been killed by Mu Qingyan.

03:45.096 --> 03:46.209
Lord Song would never harbor

03:46.220 --> 03:48.010
ambitions to dominate the Six Sects.

03:48.730 --> 03:50.980
If Yang Heying truly wanted justice,

03:50.980 --> 03:52.850
why didn't he wait for Master?

03:52.850 --> 03:54.690
Instead, he launched a sudden attack.

03:55.340 --> 03:56.980
Clearly, it was to seize the chance.

03:56.980 --> 03:58.380
What exactly does he want?

03:59.060 --> 04:00.570
Lord Song's condition

04:00.570 --> 04:01.730
shows he was being controlled.

04:03.010 --> 04:04.060
Also, Uncle Song

04:04.540 --> 04:05.380
looked fair,

04:05.780 --> 04:07.690
but he kept siding with Yang Heying.

04:07.690 --> 04:09.103
If we return to Guangtian Sect now,

04:09.410 --> 04:10.676
it would be walking into a trap.

04:10.780 --> 04:11.660
So, what should we do?

04:12.690 --> 04:13.980
All things counter each other.

04:14.850 --> 04:16.050
Just like the Shanci Mushrooms.

04:16.050 --> 04:17.936
There may be an antidote
in Blood Marsh Forest.

04:20.140 --> 04:21.810
But that place is full of monsters.

04:21.810 --> 04:22.850
They even eat people.

04:24.290 --> 04:25.130
Hurry.

04:27.100 --> 04:28.220
They can't have gone far.

04:28.220 --> 04:29.060
Search!

04:30.220 --> 04:31.340
To save Yuzhi,

04:32.220 --> 04:33.730
even a dragon's lair must be entered.

04:39.020 --> 04:40.580
They went toward Blood Marsh Forest?

04:42.170 --> 04:43.230
Send people to pursue them.

04:43.930 --> 04:45.140
Was Song Shijun captured?

04:45.410 --> 04:46.463
Pang Xiong fought fiercely

04:46.850 --> 04:48.110
and broke through the blockade.

04:48.336 --> 04:50.385
The disciples outside
tried to surround them again,

04:50.490 --> 04:51.330
but unexpectedly,

04:51.580 --> 04:52.540
Lord Cai, Lady Ning,

04:52.850 --> 04:54.660
and Mr. Dai suddenly arrived

04:55.170 --> 04:56.540
and rescued Lord Song.

04:57.580 --> 04:59.340
Why did Cai Pingchun come?

04:59.340 --> 05:01.100
Song Shijun has lost his mind.

05:01.980 --> 05:03.100
He can't say anything now.

05:23.730 --> 05:24.570
Xiaofeng,

05:25.780 --> 05:26.700
how is he?

05:26.700 --> 05:28.810
Someone injected inner power
into his meridians.

05:29.980 --> 05:31.020
It resembles the Puppet Gu,

05:32.012 --> 05:33.342
but it's formed from inner power.

05:33.353 --> 05:34.423
It can't be expelled.

05:34.900 --> 05:35.930
If this continues,

05:36.340 --> 05:38.340
Song Shijun may become a living corpse.

05:39.100 --> 05:40.233
Is there any way to cure it?

05:40.370 --> 05:41.686
He must return to Luoying Valley

05:41.730 --> 05:43.090
and slowly dissolve it with herbs.

05:43.900 --> 05:45.220
But we haven't found Zhao.

05:47.490 --> 05:48.330
Lord Cai.

05:49.660 --> 05:50.500
Uncle.

05:53.170 --> 05:54.010
Lord Cai.

05:54.290 --> 05:55.850
Uncle Pang suffered serious injuries.

05:55.850 --> 05:57.050
We've applied medicine to him.

05:57.050 --> 05:58.030
He's no longer in danger.

05:58.490 --> 05:59.330
Good.

06:00.250 --> 06:00.840
By the way,

06:00.851 --> 06:02.104
have you contacted your father?

06:03.170 --> 06:04.490
Father has received the news.

06:04.490 --> 06:05.503
He'll arrive in two days.

06:06.340 --> 06:07.180
Darn it.

06:07.340 --> 06:09.340
The Guangtian disciples
sent the wrong message.

06:09.586 --> 06:11.655
It made us run to such a distant place
for nothing.

06:11.780 --> 06:12.620
They

06:12.810 --> 06:14.310
must have deliberately lured us away.

06:14.780 --> 06:15.620
They?

06:20.660 --> 06:21.500
Uncle.

06:22.780 --> 06:23.620
Uncle.

06:36.740 --> 06:37.810
His meridians are in chaos.

06:37.810 --> 06:39.020
He must return to the valley.

06:39.290 --> 06:40.730
With Zhao's cultivation,

06:40.730 --> 06:42.243
she should be able to protect herself.

06:42.750 --> 06:43.610
Besides,

06:43.610 --> 06:44.703
Qi will arrive soon as well.

06:45.370 --> 06:46.210
Listen.

06:46.490 --> 06:47.403
Saving lives is urgent.

06:47.490 --> 06:48.543
We can only do it this way.

06:49.580 --> 06:54.140
(Blood Marsh Forest)

06:57.290 --> 06:58.660
Ahead is Blood Marsh Forest.

07:09.580 --> 07:10.920
The Curved Formation of Siqi Sect.

07:45.900 --> 07:47.020
There's a maze formation.

07:48.340 --> 07:49.180
You can't get in.

07:49.490 --> 07:50.340
How do you know?

07:50.340 --> 07:52.020
We tried several times

07:52.020 --> 07:52.930
and almost died inside.

07:52.930 --> 07:53.930
Talkative.

07:59.410 --> 08:00.250
Let's go.

08:04.120 --> 08:04.980
Zhao,

08:04.980 --> 08:06.370
they are also going to the forest.

08:06.370 --> 08:07.610
Since it's dangerous,

08:07.610 --> 08:09.356
it's better to have more people
than fewer.

08:10.370 --> 08:12.020
Yuzhi can't wait any longer.

08:12.020 --> 08:13.540
If we want to save his life,

08:13.540 --> 08:15.050
we have to follow them in.

08:17.610 --> 08:18.610
Zhao.

08:23.050 --> 08:24.270
In urgent times, we must adapt.

08:24.900 --> 08:26.053
This is the only way for now.

08:44.650 --> 08:45.490
Young Master,

08:45.890 --> 08:46.730
before it gets dark,

08:47.180 --> 08:48.220
should we go further in?

08:48.700 --> 08:49.540
I'm tired.

08:50.130 --> 08:51.530
Let's rest here for today.

08:55.890 --> 08:56.730
Young Master,

08:56.940 --> 08:59.100
Miss Cai is behind us.

09:03.580 --> 09:04.420
Zhao,

09:04.580 --> 09:06.100
should we rest here for the night

09:06.100 --> 09:06.980
and set out at dawn?

09:07.250 --> 09:08.770
I'm afraid Yuzhi won't wait.

09:09.770 --> 09:11.300
It's almost dark.

09:11.300 --> 09:13.220
The forest is dangerous by day.

09:13.220 --> 09:14.060
Going at night

09:14.850 --> 09:16.370
would be a death sentence.

09:25.980 --> 09:26.960
Let's wait until morning.

09:28.420 --> 09:29.260
Young Master,

09:29.580 --> 09:30.650
I'll gather some firewood

09:30.650 --> 09:31.490
and make a fire.

09:36.730 --> 09:37.570
I'll find

09:38.220 --> 09:39.060
some food.

09:57.420 --> 09:59.610
The poison spreads too fast on the way.

09:59.610 --> 10:01.420
We need some medicine to suppress it.

10:01.420 --> 10:03.350
But all my medicine fell
at Guangtian Sect.

10:03.350 --> 10:04.250
Zhao,

10:04.250 --> 10:05.090
what should we do?

10:23.980 --> 10:24.850
Master You,

10:25.730 --> 10:28.100
did you bring some antidotes?

10:35.730 --> 10:37.770
We are people of the demonic sect.

10:37.770 --> 10:38.750
Even if we have medicine,

10:39.010 --> 10:40.130
we dare not give it to you.

10:40.820 --> 10:42.490
If you were whipped again,

10:42.890 --> 10:44.220
we couldn't bear it.

10:44.700 --> 10:45.610
Does that make sense?

10:46.180 --> 10:47.020
Miss Cai,

10:47.530 --> 10:49.940
I know some methods to drive out poison.

10:51.420 --> 10:52.300
But...

10:52.300 --> 10:53.140
Talkative.

10:55.300 --> 10:56.250
Go if you want.

10:58.340 --> 10:59.700
Miss Cai, take this,

10:59.700 --> 11:00.540
and help me roast it.

11:28.650 --> 11:30.056
The corpse slaves at Guangtian Sect

11:30.490 --> 11:31.330
were not made by me.

11:32.370 --> 11:33.210
I know.

11:53.850 --> 11:54.690
Apply it externally.

12:37.940 --> 12:39.530
It should be fine by tomorrow night.

12:41.580 --> 12:43.650
The Six Sects appreciate it.

12:43.650 --> 12:44.980
I'll remember this favor.

12:44.980 --> 12:46.530
Mr. Song has done us a kindness.

12:46.530 --> 12:47.730
This is something we owe him.

12:57.650 --> 12:58.490
Zhao,

12:58.890 --> 12:59.890
look at this wound.

13:00.420 --> 13:01.610
From the wound,

13:02.130 --> 13:03.820
the attacker's skill is not very great,

13:04.650 --> 13:07.100
but they are very familiar with Yuzhi.

13:07.890 --> 13:09.910
They must have observed from the side,

13:09.910 --> 13:10.820
predicted

13:10.820 --> 13:12.370
Yuzhi's next move,

13:12.370 --> 13:13.980
and fired a hidden weapon.

13:13.980 --> 13:16.250
The only person capable of this

13:18.850 --> 13:19.820
is...

13:25.580 --> 13:26.420
Xingjia,

13:26.610 --> 13:27.890
you must take care of Yuzhi.

13:28.370 --> 13:29.483
I'll bring back the antidote

13:29.650 --> 13:30.820
before sunset.

13:30.960 --> 13:31.820
Okay.

13:31.820 --> 13:32.730
Zhao,

13:32.730 --> 13:33.570
be careful.

13:53.610 --> 13:55.490
Too many people are of no use.

13:56.220 --> 13:57.060
If I haven't returned

13:57.730 --> 13:58.650
by sunset,

13:59.220 --> 14:00.300
burn this forest.

14:01.060 --> 14:01.900
Yes.

14:21.010 --> 14:22.650
This is the Blood Marsh Forest.

14:33.420 --> 14:34.260
Stop.

14:49.420 --> 14:50.730
These vines have traps.

14:51.250 --> 14:52.100
There is a maze here.

14:53.850 --> 14:55.300
If the golden thread runs out

14:55.300 --> 14:56.490
and we haven't gotten out,

14:56.953 --> 14:58.306
we'll have to return the same way.

15:07.370 --> 15:08.210
Follow me.

15:35.980 --> 15:37.306
We are back at the starting point.

15:38.340 --> 15:39.986
The last bundle of thread
is almost gone.

15:40.610 --> 15:41.450
Let's go back.

15:54.980 --> 15:55.820
Zhao!

16:36.420 --> 16:37.260
Thank you.

16:37.980 --> 16:38.820
Does it hurt?

16:41.530 --> 16:42.370
Not really.

16:42.530 --> 16:43.370
I forgot long ago.

16:56.780 --> 16:58.510
♪In days gone by♪

16:58.820 --> 17:00.370
♪Willows swayed gently♪

17:00.670 --> 17:03.420
♪I first saw you in the dimness♪

17:04.390 --> 17:05.580
♪Amid the vast crowd♪

17:05.590 --> 17:07.060
♪A fleeting glance♪

17:07.230 --> 17:08.140
♪And then♪

17:08.150 --> 17:11.100
♪Love consumed me♪

17:11.910 --> 17:13.460
♪Now I think of you♪

17:14.380 --> 17:15.473
It's more dangerous inside.

17:16.140 --> 17:16.980
You go back first.

17:17.810 --> 17:18.650
I'll go alone.

17:20.010 --> 17:20.850
No.

17:21.870 --> 17:22.900
♪Scattered petals♪

17:22.910 --> 17:24.780
♪Cover the ground♪

17:24.810 --> 17:26.090
For Song Yuzhi,

17:27.106 --> 17:28.346
you'd risk yourself like this?

17:28.640 --> 17:33.320
♪Golden wind brushes the jade dew♪

17:33.490 --> 17:34.330
Don't worry.

17:35.290 --> 17:36.860
I'll bring back the antidote.

17:38.220 --> 17:39.250
Do you know the way?

17:40.980 --> 17:43.510
♪Such should be our meeting♪

17:43.790 --> 17:48.040
♪Across the Magpie Bridge♪

17:48.340 --> 17:50.920
♪Alas, peach blossoms have fallen♪

17:51.300 --> 17:54.360
♪Tears are like pearls♪

17:54.380 --> 17:55.700
When the fog cleared just now,

17:55.996 --> 17:57.490
I realized the terrain is very similar

17:57.490 --> 17:58.860
to Mu Donglie's underground palace.

17:59.530 --> 18:00.900
It confirmed my guess.

18:01.066 --> 18:02.746
It's also the formation
of Luoying Valley?

18:02.770 --> 18:04.330
Yes and no.

18:04.700 --> 18:07.090
To be precise,
it's our ancient formation.

18:07.090 --> 18:09.220
It has been changed many times,

18:09.220 --> 18:10.620
but I heard my aunt mention it.

18:11.140 --> 18:12.250
Did Ms. Cai mention

18:12.250 --> 18:13.530
a way to break the formation?

18:13.810 --> 18:14.660
She didn't,

18:14.933 --> 18:15.919
but I know the principles

18:16.180 --> 18:17.810
of the formation's changes.

18:18.700 --> 18:19.980
If I'm right,

18:19.980 --> 18:21.250
we are now here.

18:21.660 --> 18:22.500
Gen three,

18:23.010 --> 18:23.850
Dui four,

18:24.330 --> 18:25.170
Kan minus two.

18:29.490 --> 18:30.330
Follow me.

18:46.180 --> 18:47.020
Yuzhi.

18:59.220 --> 19:00.250
It's them.

19:00.980 --> 19:01.820
Yuzhi,

19:02.140 --> 19:03.250
they mean no harm.

19:03.730 --> 19:04.660
Where is Zhao?

19:05.570 --> 19:06.860
Zhao went

19:07.770 --> 19:08.900
to the forest with Mu Qingyan

19:08.900 --> 19:10.180
to find the antidote for you.

19:12.090 --> 19:13.330
Trying to trick Zhao again.

19:14.220 --> 19:15.060
Yuzhi.

19:21.250 --> 19:22.090
Yuzhi,

19:22.490 --> 19:23.980
saving your life is the priority.

19:24.330 --> 19:25.570
As for Mu Qingyan,

19:26.250 --> 19:27.730
Zhao is clever enough

19:27.730 --> 19:28.860
not to be fooled.

19:38.090 --> 19:39.050
It shouldn't be.

19:40.220 --> 19:41.770
Why is this a dead end?

19:41.770 --> 19:42.610
The path is correct.

19:43.150 --> 19:45.290
I observed the terrain from above
on the Golden Peng.

19:45.290 --> 19:47.090
To find the blood purple vine,

19:47.090 --> 19:48.530
we must pass through this forest.

19:55.620 --> 19:56.860
The fog is poisonous.

19:57.940 --> 19:58.900
Time is short.

19:59.700 --> 20:00.810
I'll clear the way for you.

20:01.490 --> 20:02.380
Mu Qingyan!

20:17.900 --> 20:18.740
Mu Qingyan!

20:19.620 --> 20:20.460
Mu Qingyan!

20:20.910 --> 20:21.770
Are you alright?

20:21.770 --> 20:22.610
Don't worry about me.

20:23.050 --> 20:24.370
- Hurry inside.
- No.

20:30.570 --> 20:31.410
Someone's coming.

20:38.860 --> 20:40.300
(Granny Jiang)

20:41.940 --> 20:42.900
Zhengyang?

20:46.290 --> 20:47.180
Pingshu?

20:49.330 --> 20:50.700
I've gone senile.

20:52.010 --> 20:54.050
You two are their children, right?

20:54.050 --> 20:54.890
Granny,

20:55.420 --> 20:56.330
you've met them?

21:14.090 --> 21:14.930
Come.

21:15.330 --> 21:16.620
Thank you, Granny Jiang.

21:17.050 --> 21:19.810
You're affected by the maze's poison.

21:20.420 --> 21:23.140
Drink this licorice decoction
for two days;

21:23.140 --> 21:25.180
the poison will naturally clear.

21:25.660 --> 21:27.010
I've already sent someone

21:27.010 --> 21:28.940
to fetch your friends.

21:29.290 --> 21:31.050
They should arrive before nightfall.

21:31.420 --> 21:33.180
His purple vine poison

21:33.180 --> 21:35.380
can only be treated
with our Night Orchid.

21:35.770 --> 21:37.220
You siblings

21:37.220 --> 21:40.490
really take after your parents.

21:40.940 --> 21:41.780
Granny Jiang,

21:42.570 --> 21:44.490
we are not siblings.

21:45.090 --> 21:47.010
The Pingshu you mentioned

21:47.530 --> 21:48.370
is my aunt.

21:49.010 --> 21:51.730
Master Zhengyang is his uncle.

21:52.330 --> 21:53.170
Then,

21:54.010 --> 21:55.860
did they eventually marry?

21:59.010 --> 21:59.900
They did,

22:00.660 --> 22:02.050
but they have both passed away.

22:04.220 --> 22:05.570
What a pity.

22:06.010 --> 22:07.770
They were so young.

22:08.940 --> 22:09.860
Granny Jiang,

22:10.620 --> 22:11.460
how did my aunt

22:11.860 --> 22:14.490
and her uncle get in?

22:15.090 --> 22:18.090
They suddenly broke in.

22:18.620 --> 22:20.090
We were all shocked

22:20.570 --> 22:23.010
and thought the maze had failed.

22:23.810 --> 22:27.380
They said Master Zhengyang's friend
had also been poisoned

22:27.730 --> 22:29.620
and needed the Night Orchid
for the remedy.

22:30.140 --> 22:31.770
We naturally agreed.

22:32.810 --> 22:36.380
After taking a few branches, they left.

22:36.940 --> 22:37.780
Granny Jiang,

22:38.660 --> 22:40.290
can we go see

22:40.570 --> 22:41.410
the Night Orchid?

22:42.050 --> 22:46.860
Yes, but don't get too close.

22:47.330 --> 22:48.180
Why?

22:48.900 --> 22:50.570
Pingshu said

22:51.420 --> 22:54.090
this must not be shown to others.

22:54.810 --> 22:56.900
Getting too close is dangerous.

22:58.250 --> 23:00.490
Didn't she also come
for the Night Orchid?

23:00.980 --> 23:02.860
Why would she say that?

23:02.860 --> 23:05.090
She said this on her second visit.

23:05.730 --> 23:07.730
After leaving with Master Zhengyang,

23:08.180 --> 23:09.570
a year and a half later,

23:09.570 --> 23:10.940
she returned and asked

23:11.420 --> 23:15.570
if Master Zhengyang had come back too.

23:16.490 --> 23:17.620
I said yes.

23:18.770 --> 23:21.180
Shortly before her return,

23:21.180 --> 23:25.330
Master Zhengyang had taken
a few more branches,

23:26.900 --> 23:30.050
and Pingshu cried.

23:31.050 --> 23:33.090
She cried so sorrowfully.

23:36.810 --> 23:38.290
Why did my aunt cry?

23:38.980 --> 23:40.250
She wouldn't say.

23:41.220 --> 23:44.220
She just reminded us
to watch over the Night Orchid.

23:44.660 --> 23:46.900
Before leaving, she set up a formation

23:47.420 --> 23:48.900
to keep people away.

23:50.010 --> 23:51.220
Why did Master Zhengyang

23:51.730 --> 23:53.490
come twice

23:54.250 --> 23:55.620
instead of taking more

23:56.620 --> 23:57.900
at once?

23:59.090 --> 24:01.420
The Night Orchid is very delicate.

24:02.220 --> 24:04.140
Once removed from the forest,

24:04.140 --> 24:08.330
it will wither like firewood
in six months,

24:08.330 --> 24:10.250
losing all medicinal properties.

24:11.620 --> 24:13.570
Our great benefactor

24:13.570 --> 24:15.810
transplanted it more than 50 times

24:15.810 --> 24:17.570
to save a few plants.

24:20.090 --> 24:21.090
Your great benefactor?

24:22.180 --> 24:24.980
That was Cai Anning.

24:24.980 --> 24:26.330
Cai Anning?

24:27.090 --> 24:29.250
She was our third demoness...

24:30.380 --> 24:31.220
our heroine.

24:34.180 --> 24:35.570
When I was a child,

24:36.900 --> 24:39.050
my mother said

24:39.050 --> 24:40.900
she was predicted at birth

24:40.900 --> 24:42.010
not to live past three.

24:43.050 --> 24:44.420
After surviving three,

24:44.980 --> 24:47.620
it was said
she wouldn't reach adulthood.

24:48.730 --> 24:51.570
So, she sought

24:52.420 --> 24:54.140
all kinds of rare herbs

24:54.620 --> 24:57.530
in the world,

24:58.290 --> 24:59.140
even stealing seeds

24:59.140 --> 25:00.940
from the Li sect.

25:00.940 --> 25:03.010
She was later pursued by the sect.

25:03.530 --> 25:05.810
Our great benefactor said

25:06.490 --> 25:10.290
she was chased here by the demonic sect.

25:12.940 --> 25:16.330
Hundreds of years ago,
the world was in chaos.

25:17.570 --> 25:19.380
We had fled here

25:19.380 --> 25:20.730
to escape the war.

25:22.050 --> 25:22.846
We thought

25:22.857 --> 25:23.831
(Cai Anning)
the vines

25:23.855 --> 25:24.529
Are you okay?

25:24.540 --> 25:25.740
(Young Jiang)
were a shield.

25:25.764 --> 25:26.290
I'm fine.

25:26.980 --> 25:28.380
But the vine's essence

25:28.380 --> 25:30.620
entered our blood

25:30.620 --> 25:31.980
and was hereditary.

25:32.660 --> 25:34.660
Not only were adults short-lived,

25:34.660 --> 25:36.900
but children were weak and bent.

25:37.180 --> 25:38.730
You have poison in your body.

25:39.330 --> 25:42.090
After learning
about our village's plight,

25:42.810 --> 25:44.380
the benefactor decided to stay

25:45.620 --> 25:47.420
and use the seeds she brought

25:47.420 --> 25:49.530
to develop a remedy.

25:49.530 --> 25:50.700
What is this?

25:50.700 --> 25:51.700
This is the Night Orchid.

25:52.290 --> 25:53.900
We plant it together.

25:53.900 --> 25:56.570
Perhaps it will cure your poison.

25:59.090 --> 26:00.700
The Night Orchid indeed neutralized

26:00.700 --> 26:03.420
the vine poison in our bodies.

26:04.810 --> 26:06.050
Unfortunately,

26:07.090 --> 26:08.860
the good times didn't last.

26:11.810 --> 26:13.380
Rumors claimed our benefactor

26:13.380 --> 26:16.290
had stolen the demonic sect's treasure

26:16.290 --> 26:17.960
- and hid it here.
- Demoness!

26:17.980 --> 26:20.430
- Many wanted to break in.
- Hand over

26:20.940 --> 26:21.980
the treasure...

26:22.490 --> 26:23.620
Hand it over...

26:23.900 --> 26:27.770
They blamed all grievances on her.

26:31.380 --> 26:33.220
She didn't defend herself

26:33.940 --> 26:36.900
but instructed us to set up
the fog and maze,

26:36.900 --> 26:38.180
sealed the Blood Marsh,

26:39.010 --> 26:42.490
and spread fearsome rumors

26:42.770 --> 26:44.420
to keep outsiders away.

26:48.330 --> 26:49.530
Soon after,

26:49.980 --> 26:52.900
our benefactor passed away.

26:57.490 --> 26:59.700
If you hadn't come here,

27:00.250 --> 27:03.570
you wouldn't have suffered such slander.

27:05.140 --> 27:06.570
I don't regret it.

27:08.290 --> 27:10.700
Saving so many people

27:12.250 --> 27:13.330
was worth it.

27:39.140 --> 27:42.420
Following her wishes,

27:42.420 --> 27:44.730
we scattered her ashes.

27:44.730 --> 27:47.010
Whenever we want to remember her,

27:47.010 --> 27:50.380
we come and see these Night Orchids.

27:50.380 --> 27:52.290
All of this was caused
by the greed of others.

27:53.940 --> 27:55.250
Why blame her

27:55.810 --> 27:56.860
and call her a demoness?

27:57.290 --> 27:58.660
It's true.

27:58.660 --> 28:01.250
It's a pity we can't leave the marsh

28:01.250 --> 28:04.050
and clear her name.

28:09.570 --> 28:10.940
Enough talking.

28:10.940 --> 28:13.220
Your friends should be here.

28:13.220 --> 28:14.140
I'll go check.

28:21.490 --> 28:22.940
The Night Orchid here,

28:22.940 --> 28:24.380
the Withered Branch of Qingque Sect,

28:24.380 --> 28:26.086
and the Beichen Orchid
of Carefree Chamber

28:27.250 --> 28:29.330
come from the same ancestral seed.

28:31.860 --> 28:33.700
I wonder if Qingque Sect's
Withered Branch

28:34.330 --> 28:35.330
has bloomed.

28:40.180 --> 28:41.020
They have,

28:42.220 --> 28:43.810
but my master used them to heal me.

28:49.810 --> 28:51.420
My master has no interest in them.

28:52.180 --> 28:53.020
But why are you

28:54.050 --> 28:55.770
so concerned about the Night Orchid?

28:56.860 --> 28:57.940
What is its true use?

29:00.620 --> 29:02.330
Why did Mu Zhengyang want it?

29:08.180 --> 29:09.020
What?

29:09.940 --> 29:11.900
Zhao and Yuzhi were captured
by the demonic sect?

29:12.250 --> 29:13.903
That day,
the Huangsha Gang lost control.

29:14.330 --> 29:16.490
Zhao and Yuzhi left with Father.

29:16.490 --> 29:17.770
Soon after, news came

29:18.140 --> 29:19.460
that the demonic sect had arrived

29:19.700 --> 29:21.050
and taken Zhao and others.

29:23.620 --> 29:24.940
It must be Mu Qingyan again.

29:25.770 --> 29:26.610
Father,

29:26.770 --> 29:27.863
have you found any evidence

29:27.874 --> 29:30.140
linking the corpse slaves
to the demonic sect?

29:33.770 --> 29:34.610
Lord Qi,

29:34.810 --> 29:35.810
is my father alright?

29:36.490 --> 29:37.790
Your father is in Luoying Valley.

29:38.090 --> 29:40.380
Lord Cai is doing his best to treat him.

29:40.380 --> 29:42.420
There is no threat to his life.

29:42.860 --> 29:43.700
That's a relief.

29:44.380 --> 29:45.220
That's a relief.

29:47.180 --> 29:48.620
Thankfully, you're fine.

29:49.140 --> 29:50.620
Yuzhi's life is safe too.

29:52.220 --> 29:53.060
Zhao,

29:53.330 --> 29:55.180
did Mu Qingyan give you a hard time?

29:55.700 --> 29:56.980
Why would he trouble me?

29:58.380 --> 30:00.900
Before, we stayed with them
because of Yuzhi.

30:00.900 --> 30:02.770
Now that we've found the antidote,

30:02.770 --> 30:04.770
let's leave once Yuzhi wakes up.

30:04.770 --> 30:07.180
We mustn't get involved with them again.

30:07.180 --> 30:08.900
What if Master finds out

30:08.900 --> 30:10.570
and locks you up for another year?

30:13.530 --> 30:14.370
We should leave.

30:16.380 --> 30:17.860
But something still feels off to me.

30:22.770 --> 30:23.610
Xingjia,

30:23.940 --> 30:24.940
watch Yuzhi.

30:25.620 --> 30:26.570
I'll go check outside.

30:37.900 --> 30:39.686
You're indeed here
to take the Night Orchid.

30:39.980 --> 30:40.820
Stop dreaming.

30:41.420 --> 30:42.940
It's protected by a formation.

30:43.220 --> 30:44.495
Only people from Luoying Valley

30:44.506 --> 30:45.330
know how to break it.

30:53.090 --> 30:54.660
The Night Orchid, like the saliva,

30:55.250 --> 30:57.330
is a medium for cultivating
the Ziwei Method,

30:58.570 --> 30:59.410
right?

31:06.730 --> 31:08.180
From the saliva

31:09.730 --> 31:10.940
to the Jade Sunflower

31:11.660 --> 31:12.980
and now the Night Orchid,

31:14.220 --> 31:15.770
it's all tied to the Ziwei Method.

31:17.010 --> 31:18.940
Mu Zhengyang used the excuse
of helping a friend

31:19.330 --> 31:20.170
to trick my aunt

31:20.490 --> 31:21.400
into getting the saliva

31:21.411 --> 31:22.684
and collecting the Night Orchid.

31:23.050 --> 31:25.140
That's why my aunt was so upset

31:25.980 --> 31:27.330
on her second visit.

31:29.900 --> 31:31.660
She had learned the truth

31:32.530 --> 31:33.440
and knew Mu Zhengyang

31:33.451 --> 31:35.240
was using her to cultivate
the Ziwei Method.

31:36.010 --> 31:37.980
But if Mu Zhengyang
has taken the Night Orchid,

31:38.940 --> 31:40.380
why come a second time?

31:40.730 --> 31:42.303
That's because the first time he took it

31:43.050 --> 31:45.050
wasn't for his own cultivation.

31:46.620 --> 31:47.980
It was offered to Nie Hengcheng.

31:50.250 --> 31:51.660
I just realized this.

31:52.570 --> 31:54.090
Mu Zhengyang told Xue Youfu

31:54.773 --> 31:56.320
he wanted to reclaim the family estate,

31:56.420 --> 31:57.880
but he couldn't defeat Nie Hengcheng.

31:58.570 --> 31:59.770
So, there was only one way:

32:01.140 --> 32:02.860
Use a peerless technique

32:04.010 --> 32:05.220
to lure Nie Hengcheng.

32:07.250 --> 32:08.980
Mu Zhengyang must've found
the Ziwei Method

32:08.980 --> 32:10.380
at the Jiuzhou Archive

32:11.380 --> 32:13.700
and used it to entice Nie Hengcheng
to practice it,

32:14.420 --> 32:15.980
even deceiving my aunt to get

32:16.570 --> 32:18.180
the Night Orchid and saliva.

32:20.620 --> 32:21.620
But I can't understand

32:22.220 --> 32:23.570
what method he used

32:24.140 --> 32:25.730
to change Nie Hengcheng's temperament,

32:26.420 --> 32:27.940
forcing all the Jianghu heroes

32:28.570 --> 32:30.090
to unite against him.

32:31.250 --> 32:32.770
As for the second trip,

32:33.570 --> 32:35.010
that's because Mu Zhengyang

32:36.290 --> 32:38.620
began practicing the Ziwei Method,

32:42.220 --> 32:43.490
just like you.

32:47.770 --> 32:49.220
Master was right.

32:50.770 --> 32:52.290
All the men in the Mu clan

32:52.290 --> 32:53.290
are skin-painted demons.

32:57.420 --> 32:58.900
I'm not Mu Zhengyang.

33:00.620 --> 33:02.380
I'll never become Nie Hengcheng.

33:02.980 --> 33:04.660
I'll never let you take
the Night Orchid.

33:06.620 --> 33:07.730
As I said,

33:08.620 --> 33:10.050
if you insist,

33:11.220 --> 33:13.330
I'll make you a ghost beneath my blade.

33:14.090 --> 33:14.930
Zhao,

33:16.940 --> 33:18.140
you can't stop me.

33:29.140 --> 33:30.700
I heard that over the past year,

33:31.380 --> 33:33.220
Song Yuzhi has been taking care of you.

33:33.570 --> 33:34.660
None of your business.

33:35.220 --> 33:37.620
Your blade is nothing special.

33:38.090 --> 33:39.330
You haven't improved.

33:39.980 --> 33:40.820
Take this.

33:58.380 --> 34:00.220
You still can't forget old feelings.

34:00.900 --> 34:02.420
I like that about you.

34:02.860 --> 34:03.940
You can't forget me,

34:04.380 --> 34:06.050
and you can't bear to kill me.

34:06.860 --> 34:07.860
Madman.

34:08.170 --> 34:09.260
Mr. Mu,

34:09.260 --> 34:10.530
are you okay?

34:23.860 --> 34:24.780
Zhao,

34:25.050 --> 34:26.490
did you quarrel?

34:27.130 --> 34:28.860
I've seen it all.

34:29.420 --> 34:30.940
Pingshu also had quarrels

34:31.210 --> 34:33.650
with Master Zhengyang,

34:33.980 --> 34:35.420
just like you two.

34:36.690 --> 34:37.900
They quarreled?

34:39.210 --> 34:40.050
What was it about?

34:40.340 --> 34:41.900
Young couples argue.

34:42.300 --> 34:43.595
It's always about who likes whom

34:43.606 --> 34:46.740
and who doesn't.

34:47.420 --> 34:48.380
But he was willing

34:48.740 --> 34:50.300
to risk his life for you,

34:50.300 --> 34:53.050
breaking through the fog and maze.

34:53.780 --> 34:56.010
That shows you mean more

34:56.010 --> 34:57.820
to him than himself.

35:03.260 --> 35:04.100
It's you again.

35:05.340 --> 35:06.980
Do you have anything to do

35:06.980 --> 35:08.210
with the corpse slaves?

35:08.210 --> 35:09.050
Hold it.

35:09.380 --> 35:10.780
Stop making baseless accusations.

35:10.780 --> 35:12.260
It was your family who did it.

35:12.260 --> 35:13.860
Why blame us?

35:13.860 --> 35:15.170
My father was framed.

35:16.170 --> 35:17.010
Mr. Song,

35:17.260 --> 35:18.820
didn't Fan tell you

35:19.010 --> 35:20.090
how you were poisoned?

35:21.820 --> 35:22.660
Yuzhi,

35:22.900 --> 35:24.206
we didn't have time to tell you.

35:24.860 --> 35:26.690
The poisoned weapon that hit you

35:26.909 --> 35:28.992
was likely used by someone
familiar with your skills

35:29.050 --> 35:30.650
and someone you didn't suspect.

35:31.490 --> 35:33.090
From the circumstances,

35:34.490 --> 35:35.820
it was most likely...

35:36.170 --> 35:37.090
Who?

35:37.090 --> 35:37.950
Tell me.

35:37.970 --> 35:38.940
Xiuzhi.

35:39.740 --> 35:40.580
My brother?

35:44.130 --> 35:45.090
It can't be him.

35:45.860 --> 35:47.090
He's not that kind of man.

35:48.900 --> 35:50.820
He's always gentle and peaceful,

35:50.820 --> 35:51.660
never aggressive.

35:52.570 --> 35:53.900
How could he do such a thing?

35:54.650 --> 35:56.090
Is it hard to understand?

35:56.090 --> 35:58.610
Everyone knows Lord Song favors you.

35:58.610 --> 36:00.650
You are Qi Yunke's disciple

36:00.650 --> 36:02.530
and Yin Qinglian's son,

36:02.530 --> 36:04.300
grandson of Yin Dai.

36:04.300 --> 36:06.010
In the future, Guangtian Sect

36:06.010 --> 36:08.090
and Qingque Sect will be yours.

36:08.090 --> 36:09.570
Now, look at your brother.

36:09.570 --> 36:12.380
His skills are inferior to yours;
his status is lower.

36:12.380 --> 36:14.900
He doesn't even know who his mother is.

36:14.900 --> 36:16.300
If he didn't remove you,

36:16.300 --> 36:18.490
when would he ever get ahead?

36:18.490 --> 36:19.650
Mr. Song,

36:19.650 --> 36:20.940
as I've told you before,

36:20.940 --> 36:23.490
the Six Sects are no good either.

36:23.490 --> 36:24.740
That day outside,

36:24.740 --> 36:26.980
Siqi Sect even used
the Curved Formation.

36:26.980 --> 36:29.780
Yang Heying is likely in cahoots
with your brother.

36:30.570 --> 36:31.490
By the way,

36:31.490 --> 36:32.650
I heard

36:32.650 --> 36:34.170
Yang Heying's daughter

36:34.780 --> 36:36.050
is marrying your brother.

36:37.740 --> 36:41.170
Truly, a loving family.

36:42.010 --> 36:42.850
Are you thirsty?

36:43.130 --> 36:43.980
Drink some water.

36:44.940 --> 36:45.780
Wait.

36:46.570 --> 36:48.010
I'll investigate

36:48.010 --> 36:49.340
the truth.

36:49.340 --> 36:51.740
The corpse slaves may have
nothing to do with you,

36:51.740 --> 36:53.980
but your appearing nearby

36:53.980 --> 36:55.130
is too much of a coincidence.

36:56.820 --> 36:58.380
What are your intentions?

36:58.659 --> 37:00.499
Our trip has nothing to do
with the Six Sects.

37:01.420 --> 37:02.260
Mr. Mu,

37:04.130 --> 37:05.170
long time no see.

37:05.780 --> 37:07.610
Last time, it was the pity ploy.

37:08.740 --> 37:11.010
I wonder
what strategy you have this time.

37:12.900 --> 37:14.900
You've become fond of joking.

37:15.380 --> 37:16.780
Have you read too many novels?

37:19.050 --> 37:19.890
Yuzhi,

37:20.610 --> 37:21.450
do me a favor.

37:25.610 --> 37:26.450
I'll go too.

37:31.610 --> 37:33.050
We should leave here asap.

37:33.050 --> 37:34.420
It's pounding

37:34.420 --> 37:35.340
in my little chest.

37:35.596 --> 37:37.076
Tonight, we return to Guangtian Sect.

37:37.380 --> 37:38.690
I must ask Xiuzhi for the truth.

37:39.090 --> 37:40.490
I wonder how Father is doing.

37:40.940 --> 37:42.650
Lord Song looks with longevity.

37:42.980 --> 37:43.980
He'll be fine.

37:44.300 --> 37:45.690
As for your brother,

37:47.050 --> 37:48.740
it has happened.

37:48.740 --> 37:49.860
Better accept it.

37:49.860 --> 37:51.490
At least we've seen his true face.

37:54.300 --> 37:55.170
I was wrong too.

37:55.170 --> 37:56.820
Knowing he's belittled by the sect

37:56.820 --> 37:58.090
due to his birth,

37:58.690 --> 38:00.090
I didn't step in to help.

38:01.860 --> 38:03.050
Even so,

38:03.050 --> 38:05.210
he shouldn't commit such atrocities

38:05.210 --> 38:06.210
and harm others.

38:07.340 --> 38:08.180
If he

38:08.780 --> 38:10.690
really colluded with Yang Heying

38:10.690 --> 38:12.570
to kill the Huangsha Gang and innocents,

38:13.380 --> 38:14.300
I'll never let him off.

38:16.380 --> 38:17.610
You're sensible.

38:19.650 --> 38:21.780
Master should be at Guangtian Sect.

38:21.780 --> 38:22.650
Then,

38:22.650 --> 38:23.740
right and wrong

38:23.740 --> 38:25.050
will be decided.

38:25.610 --> 38:26.980
Before that,

38:26.980 --> 38:29.050
I want Xingjia to do me a favor.

38:29.050 --> 38:29.890
A favor?

38:37.680 --> 38:48.340
=Generation to Generation=

39:07.100 --> 39:11.510
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

39:12.075 --> 39:16.690
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

39:17.030 --> 39:21.595
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

39:22.120 --> 39:26.420
♪Free to wander in the world♪

39:29.365 --> 39:34.065
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

39:34.590 --> 39:38.880
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

39:39.540 --> 39:43.570
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

39:43.885 --> 39:49.010
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

39:49.585 --> 39:54.395
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

39:54.610 --> 39:58.780
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

39:59.505 --> 40:03.440
♪I freely roam in the world♪

40:03.940 --> 40:09.215
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

40:31.945 --> 40:37.075
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

40:37.440 --> 40:41.810
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

40:42.075 --> 40:46.205
♪I freely roam in the world♪

40:46.390 --> 40:51.965
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
